contentrichtext.text: '''UWC''' may refer to: *[[Unanimous Written Consent]], allows a company's board of directors to take actions without a formal board meeting. *[[United World Colleges]], a group of international schools *[[University of the Western Cape]], a university in South Africa *[[University of Wisconsin Colleges]] *[[Upper Wind Chart]], used as a navigational aid in aviation *[[United Wrestling Coalition]], a wrestling promotion in Burlington County, New Jersey *[[Ulster Workers' Council]], a grouping of loyalist and unionist workers in Northern Ireland responsible for the 1974 Ulster Workers' Strike {{disambig}}
